**Mafia** | Mafia Team Group
__Basics__
Mafia is the group of the mafia team. Here the team can discuss at night who to kill.
__Members__
Mafioso
Godfather
Framer
Lawyer
Roleblocker

__Formalized__
Unique Group
Passive Start Night:
  • Create `Mafia` Poll in #Mafia
  • Unlock @Self
  • Reveal `The channel has been unlocked!` to @Self
Passive Start Day:
  • Lock @Self
  • Reveal `The channel has been locked for the day!` to @Self
On Poll Closed:
  • Process: Attack @Winner
  • Evaluate: Reveal `@Executor is attacking - @Result` to #Mafia
